::Prowl::

Prowl's mouth opens to reply to Iron Raptor's comment when he realizes he 
didn't have a good comeback. He had been to distracted by her touch on his 
hip to pay much attention to humor and think of one.

He keeps his mouth slightly open for a few seconds before closing it.

He chuckles, "Allright, you got me," he says, smiling.
